      <link>https://luigi-marini.github.io/photography/2026-05-levellers-day/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://luigi-marini.github.io/photography/2026-05-levellers-day/</guid>
        <media:content url="https://luigi-marini.github.io/photography/2026-05-levellers-day/2026-05-09-121107-Luigi-Marini-1068x1600_hu_e22b6a4ce608056d.webp" type="image/jpeg"/>
        <description>
          &lt;img src=&quot;https://luigi-marini.github.io/photography/2026-05-levellers-day/2026-05-09-121107-Luigi-Marini-1068x1600_hu_e22b6a4ce608056d.webp&quot; /&gt;
          &lt;p&gt;Levellers Day, in Burford, Oxfordshire, 9 May 2026. Held in commemoration of the execution of three Levellers in 1649, this annual political gathering stands in celebration of egualitarian movements, testimony of struggles, debate of ideas, and protest against injustice.&lt;/p&gt;
        </description></item>
